# i3 config file (v4)
#
# Please see https://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html for a complete reference!

# Requirements for my custom config:
#

# alacritty
# amixer
# compton
# copyq
# dmenu 
# dunst
# feh
# i3-gaps
# i3lock
# nm-applet
# numlockx
# polybar
# setxkbmap
# xautolock
# xrandr
# xss-lock
# xxkb
